questions.main_question: Which food delivery app do you use most frequently in India?
questions.if user gives generic answer: Can you tell me more about why you use that app?
questions.probe if needed: What factors do you consider when choosing which app to use?
questions.probe if vague: Can you provide more specific details about your experience with that app?
questions.probe gently if broad answer: Can you give me an example of a time when you used that app to order food?
